nexml.meta:
This publication re-examined 162 "scorpaeniforms" listed in Yabe (1985) and Imamura (1996). Additional specimens, including larvae, are listed in this publication. Normanichthyid specimens examined are listed in Yabe and Uyeno (1996).
Both tables 1 and 2 have been merged in one file, as both matrices compare the same characters for two taxonomic groups (Cottoid lineage in Table 1 and Zoarcoidei suborder in Table 2).
Added polymorphs. AB 10/18/12
